    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>无情的联调机器，甚至能模拟socket</p><a id="more"></a><p><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/flagged/photo-1551373916-bdaddbf4f881?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2100&q=80" alt="哈哈"></p><p><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520004434532-668416a08753?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2100&q=80" alt="xswl"></p><p>Grid Gallery:</p><div class="justified-gallery">  <!-- 加个一空行，否则不会渲染markdown --><p>  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/flagged/photo-1551373916-bdaddbf4f881?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2100&q=80" alt="哈哈"><br>  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520004434532-668416a08753?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2100&q=80" alt="xswl"></p></div><p>要求不多，和<a href="https://pro.ant.design/">antd-pro</a>一样就行</p><ol><li><p>首先clone<a href="https://github.com/domeafavour/mock">项目</a>到本地</p></li><li><p>进入项目目录，执行<code>npm install</code>或者<code>npm i</code></p></li><li><p>执行<code>npm run server</code></p></li><li><p>访问<a href="http://localhost:8888">http://localhost:8888/</a>后面跟接口名称</p></li><li><p>在<code>mock</code>文件夹下创建文件，内容如：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">module</span>.exports = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">'POST /api/user/login'</span>: <span class="function">(<span class="params">req, res, next, mockjs</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> &#123; username, password &#125; = req.body;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (username === <span class="string">'admin'</span> &amp;&amp; password === <span class="string">'admin'</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      res.json(&#123; <span class="attr">success</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>, <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="string">'ok'</span> &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      res.json(&#123; <span class="attr">success</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>, <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="string">'wrong username or password'</span> &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改代理域名为<a href="http://localhost:8888">http://localhost:8888</a>，访问创建的接口：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> login = <span class="keyword">async</span> (username, password) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> response = <span class="keyword">await</span> fetch(<span class="string">'/api/user/login'</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    method: <span class="string">'POST'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    body: <span class="built_in">JSON</span>.stringify(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      username,</span><br><span class="line">      password,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">    headers: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="string">'Content-Type'</span>: <span class="string">'application/json; charset=utf-8'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> &#123; success &#125; = <span class="keyword">await</span> response.json();</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (success) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'登录成功'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="注意"><a href="#注意" class="headerlink" title="注意"></a>注意</h3><ol><li>暂时不支持mock下创建文件夹</li></ol>]]></content>
    
